{"tid":863952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"迫巴士比隻米奇豬閪激親","createTime":"2018-10-16T01:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T01:59:28.000Z","uid":169620,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c54cbf4065b88e9ae6c07129d4d5d5c037120b42","tid":863952,"uid":169620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/16/094418_0c8bea3d39aae4a9dcb65785327a9eed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F16%2F094418_0c8bea3d39aae4a9dcb65785327a9eed.jpg&h=37f3fff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我早佢一個站上車，<br />\n架巴士本身都已經爆哂想比錢都唔係咁昜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條豬西一上到黎就係咁講「點解唔行入去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？」<br />\n講左兩三次加埋個西臉，我就問「你想點行入去呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n佢仲好意思話「我又無叫你行，我話我想行入去之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n好心咁撚迫就講少句野唔好煩啦，<br />\n個個都迫到無位郁仲嘈撚住哂，<br />\n影衰哂香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （唔知佢係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n一齊分享下今日撘車經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}